      "content": "that sounds really intense and scary. honestly i'm kind of worried i might have already messed up. i took a dose this morning and i've been feeling a bit shaky and my heart is racing a little bit. is that just the anxiety from the finals or could it be something serious from the combination? what should i do right now?",
